Diagnostic operations verifying

//axvo_group axd_tabtarget
{rbtgog_ark}::
Operations on
{rbtga_ark}
units: abjuration, conjuring, grafting, about assembly, vouching, summoning, inspection, and hallmark checking.

[[rbtgog_sa]]
//axvo_group axd_tabtarget
{rbtgog_sa}::
